\v 32 Zoz…Ыfe ma …†aeiti Izilay…Ыle nuiti ti  Лaani ga tiye, ti ze…†e ga tiye Ezipete yooi zu, ti naati maa…†uluni Sik…Ыme taazu Л…Ы, zou goi naa zu, nii Zak…Ф…Уe geyani ga wali …†ae ungila (100), ∆Уam…Ф…Фl mavofodaiti ma, nii eћБ …†…Ыni ga Sik…Ыme k…Ы…Ы…†…Ы. NaћБ …†…Ы…Ыni ga Zoz…Ыfe mavofodaiti t…Фn…Ф ma yooi ta.
